  "detailed_description": "<strong>Blast through generated worlds!</strong><br>The carefully designed caves of Vector Prospector are completely unique every time you play, and are a dangerous test of both your wits and your skills.<br><br>Can you collect the five green gems and escape alive?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/7e35a9f9c68f5aa7d97ceb16b0ba812c.poster.avif?t=1605961778\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/7e35a9f9c68f5aa7d97ceb16b0ba812c.webm?t=1605961778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/7e35a9f9c68f5aa7d97ceb16b0ba812c.mp4?t=1605961778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>You will die. A lot.</strong><br>Vector Prospector is easy to learn and tough to master with a streamlined movement system that only uses four buttons: left, right, move, and shoot.<br>Make sure to not crash into the cave walls! Or the enemies. Or the spikes. Or the falling blocks. And don’t get shot. Or run out of energy...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/f395045e9378da6462239723f5f38558.poster.avif?t=1605961778\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/f395045e9378da6462239723f5f38558.webm?t=1605961778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/f395045e9378da6462239723f5f38558.mp4?t=1605961778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>    <br><strong>Unlock powerups and ships to expand your game over time</strong><br>Unlock ships like the Sniper to slow down time, or the Collector to carefully construct and deploy powerup combos at the perfect moment.<br>Combine Triple Shot and Quad Shot to shoot twelve bullets at once!<br>Stack and combine multiple powerups in creative ways to survive your encounter with the final Guardian of the Gems.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/18efea4d5f4a80025e1df2b22df44a9d.poster.avif?t=1605961778\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/18efea4d5f4a80025e1df2b22df44a9d.webm?t=1605961778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/18efea4d5f4a80025e1df2b22df44a9d.mp4?t=1605961778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Easy to learn, tough to master<br></li><li> Challenging procedural and fully destructible caves<br></li><li> Use the environment to outsmart and turn your enemies against each other<br></li><li> Concoct thousands of powerful powerup combinations!<br></li><li> Secret unlockable game mode</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/775775b4d721f19a54704c80e743fbae.poster.avif?t=1605961778\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/775775b4d721f19a54704c80e743fbae.webm?t=1605961778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145950/extras/775775b4d721f19a54704c80e743fbae.mp4?t=1605961778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
